{"id":613162,"date":[{"year":1981,"month":5,"day":10}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"五月诗抄","genre":"","count":"123","ytitle":"","mtitle":"雨夜，天放晴","ftitle":"","authors":["黎焕颐"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎焕颐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朦朦胧胧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗两颗……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暖风拂天际，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点燃满天星火1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好!霖雨扑不灭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风吹又着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵!天上有这么多的火种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而窃火者，为什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有普罗米修士一个?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我问静夜，静夜沉默。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有原野灯光闪烁……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，灯光正闪烁地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出对窃火者的倾慕。"}]}